      "parameters": {
        "content": "## FLOW 4: Registration + Email Confirmation & Resend\nMirrors the app's Supabase Auth signup (script.js handleRegister / resendConfirmation).\n\n- **Register** calls Supabase Auth `/auth/v1/signup`, passing the profile fields as user metadata and `redirect_to` as the confirmation link target. Supabase then sends the branded \"Confirm signup\" email.\n- **Resend Confirmation** calls Supabase Auth `/auth/v1/resend` (type=signup) to send a fresh confirmation link.\n\nNOTE: the confirmation email is sent and templated by Supabase (Authentication > Emails > Templates), NOT by n8n. n8n only triggers it. The `apikey` header uses the publishable (anon) key.",
        "height": 536,
